# Implementation Plan: Update Mock Data to Ecommerce

This plan outlines the transition of the Adecos MVP mockup data from a general-purpose mix (Forex, Crypto, Finance) to a dedicated E-commerce and Retail focus. This includes updating the documentation, backend generators, and frontend static mock data.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This change will replace all existing mock programs (Exness, Binance, Sephora, etc.) with new E-commerce focused programs (Shopee, Lazada, Amazon, etc.). Historical data will be preserved but the names and niches will change.

## Proposed Changes

### Documentation (docs/)
#### [MODIFY] [PRD.md](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/docs/PRD.md)
* Update User Personas and Stories to focus on E-commerce/Retail Marketers.
* Update feature descriptions to mention E-commerce affiliate programs.

#### [MODIFY] [SRS.md](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/docs/SRS.md)
* Update mock data examples in the JSON structure and Data Model sections to use ecommerce values.

---

### Backend (backend/)
#### [MODIFY] [mock_data_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/backend/mock_data_generator.py)
* Update `PROGRAMS_AND_NICHES` to include Shopee, Lazada, Tiki, Amazon, TikTok Shop, Shopify.
* Remove Forex and Crypto entries.
* Update metric generation logic to better reflect ecommerce ROAS/CPC (lower CPC, higher CR).

#### [MODIFY] [intent_classifier.py](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/backend/intent_classifier.py)
* Update the `CLASSIFIER_PROMPT` examples to use E-commerce programs (e.g., "Shopee", "Amazon") instead of "Binance".

---

### Frontend (frontend/src/data/)
#### [MODIFY] [mockAdsData.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/data/mockAdsData.js)
* Replace all campaigns in `mockCampaigns` with E-commerce campaigns (e.g., "Shopee 11.11 Flash Sale", "Amazon Holiday Tech").
* Update keywords and program names.

#### [MODIFY] [mockAdsManager.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/data/mockAdsManager.js)
* Update account names in `mockAccounts` to ecommerce themes (e.g., `MDW_Shopee_VN_01`).

#### [MODIFY] [mockCryptoAffiliates.js](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos-mvp-mockup/frontend/src/data/mockCryptoAffiliates.js)
* Update the content to be E-commerce affiliate programs.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
* I will run the backend and check the `/api/chat/thinking` and `/api/research/stream` endpoints to ensure they return the new ecommerce data.
* I will use the browser tool to navigate to the "Quản lý tài khoản" page and verify the table shows ecommerce accounts and campaigns.

### Manual Verification
1. Open the Chat interface and ask "Tìm kiếm các chương trình affiliate về thời trang". Verify the results show ecommerce programs.
2. Navigate to "Quản lý tài khoản ads" and verify "Shopee", "Lazada", etc. are present instead of "Exness".
3. Check the Dashboard page to ensure charts are rendering with the new campaign names.
